com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":467239629,"title":"为什么现在魂类游戏开始崛起了，动作游戏却开始没落了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/467239629","type":"question","created":1624548470,"answer_count":78,"follower_count":114,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,75244,725189],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"同样是硬核类游戏，为何魂类强势崛起，动作游戏却开始没落了。魂类游戏的优势在那里呢。动作游戏的出路又在那里呢。我本人只玩过只狼一个魂类游戏，选择他的原因也很简单，就是操作性比其他魂类游戏要高，招式多一点，我甚至是把他当动作游戏玩的，几周目过后，像鬼泣一样是想着怎么秀boss的。我觉得动作游戏没落的原因是体量不够大，后劲不足。就如我最爱的鬼泣，感觉内容太少了，地方太少，要是有一个开放世界的体量，像暗黑血统那样，同时保留鬼泣的动作性，后续不间断更新一下，我相信会好不少，就如那次更新维吉尔一样。如果现在多更新两个人物，或者一些新关卡，我相信会好不少，资金足够这个系列长远发展。开放合作也是一个不错的选择，不知道为何这次没有完整的做出来。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Its2tlZy2isRwEAMaCDY2MTEwNjM0IPbI0oYGMAA4ckAFcgk0NjcyMzk2Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"68 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-97a4a4ef7c54338d399ff9ac35c1891f_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1723207260.84006","card_id":"Q_663692819","target":{"id":663692819,"title":"经典文学中哪些爱情在今天看来更像是「恋爱脑」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663692819","type":"question","created":1723024736,"answer_count":17,"follower_count":27,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2058,4729,23196,23486,3625361],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Its2tlZy2isRwEAMaCTEwOTc2NTAxMCDgis21BjAAOBtABnIJNjYzNjkyODE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"68 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0d46a262eaba49084b798ffd90f001da_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1723207260.84160","card_id":"Q_663784496","target":{"id":663784